# IDE / local
.vscode/

# Python caches and virtual envs
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/venv/
**/venv_*/
**/.venv/
**/site-packages/

# Environments
**/.env
**/.env.*

# Logs / runtime artifacts
**/*.log
**/*.jsonl
app/memory/
tmp/
brain/runtime/
brain/platform/docker/docker-data/

# Secrets: ignore all by default, keep only safe metadata/templates
**/secrets/**
!**/secrets/**/
!**/secrets/.gitignore
!**/secrets/README.md
!**/secrets/index.yaml
!**/secrets/**/*.template
!**/secrets/**/*.example
!**/secrets/**/SETUP_GUIDE.md

# Keep GitHub example but never commit real token file
brain/secrets/system/github/github.env
